        {
            "title": "A股半日逾1%  深股跌幅大",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A股半日逾1%，深股曾跌逾2%，創板收跌1.78%，兩市成交合計112253.66億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"A股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/05/20250408_FI_source-ap_AShare-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"A股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/05/20250408_FI_source-ap_AShare-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">A股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬綜指半日收報3,830，跌46點或1.2%，早段見3,861，跌15點或0.38%，為半日，跌幅隨即擴大，尾段低見3,822，跌54點或1.39%，半日成交5,693.94億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深成指半日收報13,873點，跌249點或1.77%，早段見14,061，跌62點或0.43%，為半日高位，隨即反覆向下，臨近收市低見13,800，挫323點或2.28%，半日成交6559.72億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300半日跌55點或1.17%，報4672點 ; 創業板指數跌63點或1.78%，報3511點。</p>\n</div>",
